            <scopecontent id="aspace_ec0c1907316f519933424a0d90509fb3">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Business Papers consist chiefly of retained carbons of outgoing correspondence to clients and associates and newspaper clippings, documenting in particular Lazarus's work with three tribes: the Tuscarora Nation, the Blackfeet Tribe, and the Seneca Nation. Lazarus's work with other clients and cases is also documented in the correspondence and clippings.</p>
